<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Saddle Ridge</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">A beautiful residential neighborhood located within the North-east quadrant of Calgary, Alberta, Saddle Ridge is bound by the 36 Street E on the west, the McKnight Blvd on the south, the 68 Street E on the east and the 96 Avenue N on the north.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">The community in Saddle Ridge was originally established as acreages that were eventually <span class="par-xl">urbanized in the late 1990s into the well-planned neighborhood that we see today</span>.</p>
        </div>
